Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: csrmesh
Version: 0.10.0
Summary: Reverse engineered implementation of the CSRMesh bridge protocol
Home-page: https://github.com/nkaminski/csrmesh
Author: Nash Kaminski, Tomas Salfischberger
Author-email: nashkaminski@kaminski.io, tomas@salfischberger.nl
License: LGPLv3
Description: Reverse engineered implementation of the CSRMesh bridge protocol. Currently only capable of interfacing with Feit HomeBrite smart bulbs and MOVE controller. Support for additional devices can easily be added. Requires bluez gatttool to transmit packets.
Keywords: bluetooth csrmesh qualcomm csr BTLE
